data.description: Spacious four bedroom home with tons of updates! Brand new kitchen w/ soft close cabinets, granite countertops & stainless steel appliances. Open floor plan. Family room on lower level with with beautiful fireplace. Newer furnace, ac, hot water tank, roof. Private fenced in backyard. Large patio with hot tub!
